                 <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5월 22일은 부처님오신날입니다~<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">그래서,<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">저희 이수한의원이 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 47, 34);\" class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b>5월21일~22일 (월,화)은 휴진</b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">이고<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>5월23일(수)은 오후 2시부터 진료</b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">를 합니다.</span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"> <br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">아!<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">수요일은 원래 문학진원장님께서 오후 진료는 안하시자나요?<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">하지만<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>5월23일 수요일은</b><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>문학진 원장님 &amp; 나효석 원장님 두분 다</b><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>오후 2시부터 7시까지 함께 진료 하십니다</b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.</span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">그러니<span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">이수한의원으로 내원하시는&nbsp;<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">모든<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">환자분들께서는<br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">진료 이용에 꼭 참고하세요~</span></span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1526616050672-572498213_image_0_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aa0789ff28719603.png\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1526616050672-572498213_image_0_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aa0789ff28719603.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aa0789ff28719603.png\" data-width=\"1045\" data-height=\"777\" width=\"1045\" height=\"777\" data-attachment-id=\"IKjwwkbEomGDyowXmEP2jBMmWN9U\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    